{"_path":"/resident/r013","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"建構林梢公園","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r013-11.jpeg","sequence":13,"category":"環保","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-07-31T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"在被森林環抱的-a7-重劃區-建構林梢公園"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在被森林環抱的 A7 重劃區 - 建構林梢公園"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"主題"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主題:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在森林環抱的 A7 重劃區, 讓我們擁抱森林 建構林梢步道。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"說明"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"說明:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區整體而言缺乏公園綠地, 尤其是未來建案不斷帶來大量居民的中心商業區, 文青國小生活圈及原有的體育大學生活圈。 使用滯洪池活化也只能帶來極其少量的綠地！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"但在(如下圖紅色框中) 公滯 02, 公滯 07 及 公園 23 預定地所在範圍 是十八份坑溪上游, 擁有森林但地形坡度緩和。 應該仿造新北五股觀音山林梢步道。讓 A7 重劃區的中心商業區的上班族及文青國中小學生能有擁抱森林的機會。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r013-12.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r013-12.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"辦法"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"辦法;"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在下圖紅框區域 整併公園 23 預定地及公滯 02 區域，建立林梢步道。因地形坡度和緩不會造成環境生態破壞！ 也完全不影響防洪治水。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓居民能於此區域享受芬多精森林浴。讓中心商業區上班族能於午休來此休息。 文青國中小學童能藉由此步道往來於合宜住宅及學校。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"將公滯 07 打造成為小型運動公園, 讓文青國中小學生有社區運動場所。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望有議員能統籌推動，讓市府先有評估作業。將會是 CP 值極高的 宜居城市投資。有效解決居民缺乏公園綠地的問題。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"市府也可利用市長強調的 BIM 做設計規劃, 落實市府數位轉型-智慧城市規劃能量。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r013-13.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r013-13.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r013-14.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r013-14.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓我們的孩子上學就是 享受森林浴！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r013-11.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r013-11.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"讓居民走路到全聯/家樂福也能通個林梢步道享受芬多精。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"在被森林環抱的-a7-重劃區-建構林梢公園","depth":2,"text":"在被森林環抱的 A7 重劃區 - 建構林梢公園","children":[{"id":"主題","depth":3,"text":"主題:"},{"id":"說明","depth":3,"text":"說明:"},{"id":"辦法","depth":3,"text":"辦法;"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:resident:r013.md","_source":"content","_file":"resident/r013.md","_extension":"md"}